message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you this amazing product! I think it's a great opportunity for you to get your hands on it. I'm willing to sell it to you for $130.
Thank you for the offer, Alice. I appreciate the opportunity to purchase this product. I would like to counteroffer at $120.
Thank you for your counteroffer, Bob. I understand that you're trying to get a good deal, but I'm not willing to go that low. I'm willing to meet you halfway and offer the product to you for $135.
I appreciate your willingness to negotiate, Alice. Considering my budget, I would like to counteroffer at $125.
I understand that you're trying to stay within your budget, Bob. However, I'm still not willing to go as low as $125. I'm willing to offer you a compromise at $132.50. This is the best I can do.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I will counteroffer at $127.50.

Thank you for your offer, Alice. I will counteroffer at $129.
